```

### Instructions to Customize
1. Replace placeholders like `[Your Field or Major]`, `[Your University]`, and `[Year]` with your information.
2. Add your own skills, projects, and education details.
3. Modify the design by tweaking the CSS in the `<style>` section to fit your personal style.

This template is fully responsive and should look good on both desktop and mobile devices.
